reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfy, quality fabric
reviews.reviewText: Love the style, legs loose enough at ankles to not be your typical legging. Very comfy, not to tight, pockets are great and great for exercise or everyday.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent yoga pants!!
reviews.reviewText: Thick fabric that moves with you. I think even white underwear wouldn’t show!We have a litter of puppies that have just discovered they can grab things. The puppies grabbed the fabric over my calf but the material stretched instead of getting punctured and ripping.I’m short so they are bit long in the leg for me but that just gave my heavy thighs extra material to stretch in.Best, least restrictive leggings I have bought in a long time.Also the phone pockets on both thighs are excellent! Large enough to hold a big phone when you need to and blends into the design so the pocket isn’t visible until you use it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great Pants but.....
reviews.reviewText: These pants fit amazing along with being extremely comfortable. I love the side pockets! The only issue I have is the "smell" of these pants. Is anyone experiencing a type of chemical smell? I can't describe the smell, but it's not appealing and I have washed all 6 pairs that I have multiple times and the smell will not go away. It's the most bizarre thing I've ever experienced in purchasing clothing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars On my 3rd purchase
reviews.reviewText: Love these! They are great quality, you can’t see through them and are one of my favorites! I’ve bought 3 of these and I will be buying more. I’m 5’10 and wear a 16/18 and get the XL size. They aren’t short on me and have a comfortable stretch. I did buy a cheaper brand after my first purchase and regretted it. This is the brand to go with without a doubt! Don’t waste money on other brand!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So comfy and stretchy! Perfect fit!
reviews.reviewText: I have 4 pairs of these leggings and I reach for them more than any other of my leggings. They fit perfectly and comfortably every single time. They are high-waisted, which is good for us bigger women. AND the have pockets in the perfect place. I recommend these 100%.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Depends what you are looking for
reviews.reviewText: If you are looking for compression, these have absolutely none. The material is high waisted and does not feel like it would roll down but it's thin...you can see any dimpling/cellulite, etc. The material is very soft and not shiny. For reference, I'm 5'3" and these were way too long so there was too much bunched fabric and threading that was sticking out. It's a full length legging. Unfortunately, these are going back.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very comfortable and I love the pockets!!
reviews.reviewText: I’m just getting ready to go to the Y and these leggings will work out so great. I love the pockets, deep enough to secure my iPhone 14!! And a great price

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: As a plus size lady I find it hard to find leggings that are comfy, high waisted, not see through, and flattering around my curves. THESE ARE IT! I own 10 pairs! They are so comfy, have lots of stretch while still remaining tight enough to hug my curves without falling down. They don’t lost color in the wash either. Plus a pocket!!! Can’t get enough of these!

I bought a pair of these and after wearing them for a couple of days, I bought 2 more!The best part is that they stay put! I find that a lot of the high waisted tights slide/roll down, constantly needing to be adjusted, and sizing down will usually dig into my back when sitting, but not these!They stay in place, don't dig in the back, they're so soft and the perfect medium weight to keep you warm but still be lightweight and breathable.I love that they can be dressed up or down. Most tights with pockets have really obvious seams that make them look like athletic wear but not these, you can easily wear them with a nice sweater to go out. I will be wearing these on a flight next month as they are the most comfy and versatile pants I own.Also, no need to size up. They fit true to size.I hope they come up with more colors, so I can buy all of them!
